6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to definitions and general
provisions; amending 25 O.S. 2021, Section 106, which
8 relates to newspapers; defining term; prescribing
requirements; imposing duties upon periodical and
9 non-periodical newspapers; imposing restrictions
based on geographical location; modifying certain
10 publication provisions; modifying provisions related
to excusable failure with respect to continuity of
11 publication; and providing an effective date.
