16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 25 O.S. 2021, Section 106, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 106. No legal notice, advertisement, or publication of
19 any kind required or provided for by the laws of this state to be
20 published in a newspaper of general circulation shall have force or
21 effect unless published in a legal newspaper of the county in this
22 state. Legal newspapers shall be either:
23 A. PERIODICAL PERMIT NEWSPAPER: A legal newspaper of the county
24 is any newspaper of general circulation which, during a period of
