1 gene ral local news relevant to the area the notice is intended to
2 serve, reports of local events and persons, local government
3 proceedings, feature stories, graphics, photographs, letters to the
4 editor or editorial pages. No non-periodical newspaper shall
5 knowingly carry advertisements which are prohibited by state or
6 federal law;
7 4. Has maintained a known office of publication in the county
8 where the business of the publication can be transacted with the
9 public, and where the public can personally interact or meet with
10 local staff of the publication;
11 5. Has published in the newspaper an annual statement of
12 ownership, management, and circulation in the issue dated nearest
